34#ifndef _LOGGER_H
35#define _LOGGER_H
36
37struct log {
38 int head;
39 int siz;
40 char **buf;
41 time_t *tbuf;
42 char *fname;
43};
44
45extern struct log *log_open __P((size_t, char *));
46extern void log_add __P((struct log *, char *));
47extern int log_print __P((struct log *, char *));
48extern int log_vprint __P((struct log *, const char *, ...));
49extern int log_vaprint __P((struct log *, const char *, va_list));
50extern int log_close __P((struct log *));
51extern void log_free __P((struct log *));
52
53#endif /* _LOGGER_H */
